divs: sighting detailsi got something i think you might be interested in. again while viewing the hazecam.net site a short time ago (it is now 5:26 pm eastern time) i was viewing the newark\new york cam when i saw 2 unknowns. one may be a blimp (the lower one) i'm not sure. the one near the plane in my opinion cannot possibly be a plane because they are too near each other. judging by the closeness of the 2 craft, and the fact that it is a jumbo jet being directed by a control tower from either jfk international or newark international that would be considered a near miss. in any event i am at a loss as to what it or in fact they may be. it seems i have been seeing a lot of unknowns on the hazecam.net site (i have several that are in my files right now)
